title: David Leadbetter - Golf - From Beginner to Winner
description:
The majority of golfers around the world are weekend players and
those whose game needs a refresher. This instructional disc from
David Leadbetter, one of the sport&#039;s most famous coaches, is 
aimed at just those groups. In this easy to follow program that
involves no complex theories, Leadbetter covers basic lessons,
including the mini-swing, adding distance off the tee, rythm
and flow, and club choice.  Your game will get better.  
Good golfing and good day.
